 S' R' U R S R2' S2 R U' R' S2 R) (R' D R U' R D' R' U R D R' U R' D' R U')\"><strong>(R S' R' U R S R2' S2 R U' R' S2 R) (R' D R U' R D' R' U R D R' U R' D' R U')</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Converting Example</strong></p><p><a href=\"/tutorial/epll\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">EPLL</a> and CPLL algs are helpful.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>X+ -&gt; G-<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">-&gt;<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PLL-U- F D+</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(M2' U M U2 M' U M2') U (R S' R' U R S R2' S2 R U' R' S2 R) U' (R' D' R U R' U' R U R' D R U' R' U R U')\"><strong>(M2' U M U2 M' U M2') U (R S' R' U R S R2' S2 R U' R' S2 R) U' (R' D' R U R' U' R U R' D R U' R' U R U')</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>F2L转换机: 换位子打乱</strong></p><p>主要用于以下情形: 统一地生成F2L情况; 从某个F2L情况开始, 绕过还原它的步骤, 直接转换为新的F2L情况; 生成F2L情况并保留尽可能多的块 (例如多组入槽, EOLS, <a href=\"/tutorial/ols\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">OLS</a>等情况); 不熟悉常规的F2L打乱公式.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>转换机</strong></p><p>公式来自三盲的三循环棱 (角) 和翻转公式.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>E+<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>E-<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-convertors/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>F<img src=\"/st